================================================================================
Third-Party Components
================================================================================

@blamejs/stash ships with zero npm dependencies -- runtime and development --
and vendors no third-party code in the published package. Hashing and random
identifier generation run entirely on Node's built-in node:crypto.

The documentation example app (examples/wiki, never published) vendors the
Prism syntax highlighter under examples/wiki/public/vendor/ with its original
license and a pinned SHA-256 manifest.
